Beyond Westworld is a 1980 television series that carried on the stories of the two feature films Westworld and Futureworld .
It featured Jim McMullan as Security Chief John Moore of the Delos Corporation .
The story revolved around John Moore having to stop the evil scientist , Quaid , as he planned to use the robots in Delos to try to take over the world .
Despite being nominated for two Primetime Emmy Awards -LRB- Outstanding Achievement in Makeup and Outstanding Art Direction For a Series -RRB- , only five episodes were produced , and only three of them were aired before cancellation .